{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"StorageEstimate","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/conflicting/Web/API/StorageManager/estimate","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Storage_API\">Storage API</a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/StorageManager\"><code>StorageManager</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>方法</summary><ol><li><em><code>estimate()</code></em></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/StorageManager/persist\"><code>persist()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/StorageManager/persisted\"><code>persisted()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Related pages for Storage</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Navigator/storage\"><code>Navigator.storage</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WorkerNavigator/storage\"><code>WorkerNavigator.storage</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"><div class=\"notecard secure\" id=\"sect2\"><p><strong>安全上下文:</strong> 此项功能仅在<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/Security/Secure_Contexts\">安全上下文</a>(HTTPS), 一些 <a href=\"#browser_compatibility\">支持的浏览器</a>.</p></div></div>\n\n<div id=\"sect3\">&nbsp;</div>\n\n<p><strong><code>StorageEstimate</code></strong>&nbsp;提供对你的域名或Web app的数据存储空间总量和已用量的估计值,该对象实例由<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/StorageManager\"><code>StorageManager</code></a>的<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/StorageManager/estimate\" title=\"estimate()\"><code>estimate()</code></a> 方法返回的<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Promise\"><code>Promise</code></a>返回.</p>\n\n<p>这些值仅为估计值有多种原因,既有对性能的考虑,也有防止将其作为指纹(fingerprinting)的目的.详情请参看属性.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"属性","title":"属性","isH3":false,"content":"<p><em>该对象目前总是同时包含以下两个属性.</em></p>\n\n<dl>\n <dt id=\"quota_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/StorageManager/estimate\"><code>quota</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> <span class=\"notecard inline secure\" title=\"此功能仅在安全上下文（HTTPS）中可用\">安全上下文</span></dt>\n <dd>用户设备为你的域名或Web&nbsp;app预留的存储空间总大小,且该大小为估计值.虽然实际上可能有比这更多的存储空间,但这时你不应使用那多余的部分.</dd>\n <dt id=\"usage_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/StorageManager/estimate\"><code>usage</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> <span class=\"notecard inline secure\" title=\"此功能仅在安全上下文（HTTPS）中可用\">安全上下文</span></dt>\n <dd>你的域名或Web&nbsp;app已经使用的存储空间大小,且该大小为估计值.剩余可用空间请综合quota属性计算.</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"规范","title":"规范","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Specification</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Comment</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://storage.spec.whatwg.org/#dictdef-storageestimate\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Storage<br><small lang=\"zh-CN\">StorageEstimate</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-living\">Living Standard</span></td>\n   <td>Initial definition.</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"浏览器兼容性","title":"浏览器兼容性","isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect4\"><div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect5\"><strong><a href=\"https://github.com/mdn/browser-compat-data\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">We're converting our compatibility data into a machine-readable JSON format</a></strong>.\n            This compatibility table still uses the old format,\n            because we haven't yet converted the data it contains.\n            <strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/MDN/Structures/Compatibility_tables\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Find out how you can help! (en-US)</a></strong></div>\n\n<div class=\"htab\" id=\"sect6\">\n    <a id=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\" name=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\"></a>\n    <ul>\n        <li class=\"selected\"><a href=\"#compat-desktop\">Desktop</a></li>\n        <li><a href=\"#compat-mobile\">Mobile</a></li>\n    </ul>\n</div></div>\n\n<div id=\"compat-desktop\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Feature</th>\n   <th>Chrome</th>\n   <th>Firefox (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>Internet Explorer</th>\n   <th>Microsoft Edge</th>\n   <th>Opera</th>\n   <th>Safari (WebKit)</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Basic support</td>\n   <td>55</td>\n   <td><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/57\" title=\"Released on 2017-11-28.\">57</a> (57)</td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td>42</td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n\n<div id=\"compat-mobile\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Feature</th>\n   <th>Android Webview</th>\n   <th>Chrome for Android</th>\n   <th>Firefox Mobile (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>IE Mobile</th>\n   <th>Opera Mobile</th>\n   <th>Safari Mobile</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Basic support</td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td>55</td>\n   <td>57.0 (57)</td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td>42</td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"相关链接","title":"相关链接","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Storage_API\">Storage API</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/StorageManager\"><code>StorageManager</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/StorageManager/estimate\"><code>StorageManager.estimate()</code></a></li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Navigator/storage\"><code>navigator.storage</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"属性","id":"属性"},{"text":"规范","id":"规范"},{"text":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性"},{"text":"相关链接","id":"相关链接"}],"summary":"StorageEstimate 提供对你的域名或Web app的数据存储空间总量和已用量的估计值,该对象实例由StorageManager的estimate() 方法返回的Promise返回.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"StorageEstimate","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/conflicting/web/api/storagemanager/estimate","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/conflicting/web/api/storagemanager/estimate/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/conflicting/Web/API","title":"指数"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/conflicting/Web/API/StorageManager/estimate","title":"StorageEstimate"}],"pageTitle":"StorageEstimate | MDN","noIndexing":true}}